{"tid":2231454,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"夜晚好想食譚仔皮蛋點算，自己整！","createTime":"2020-10-05T16:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T05:32:21.000Z","uid":68594,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"954c8dd082007c9627faab4a8452903a08311605","tid":2231454,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"大家好！我係子言張！<br />\n<br />\n突然之間心血來潮好想夜麻麻整個皮蛋食😂<br />\n<br />\n但係譚仔又閂咗門，唯有自己落手整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kMcSO94A0V4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkMcSO94A0V4&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZLwzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=2f081539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kMcSO94A0V4</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw!鍾意我呢段片嘅朋友可以俾個like我啦或者可以訂閱我嘅Channel嘅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔴材料<br />\n皮蛋..............2隻<br />\n芫茜..............1紥<br />\n青尖椒............半隻<br />\n指天椒............1隻<br />\n蒜頭..............5-6瓣<br />\n<br />\n🔴調味料<br />\n浙江醋、麻油、生抽、麻辣紅油、鹽、糖、雞粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypGddLj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypGddLj.png&h=d399dfe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔴(處理皮蛋)步驟：<br />\n1.搓走皮蛋外層的灰、敲碎外層，用清水把皮蛋沖洗乾淨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234726_67e788b63bab12154aa9cbd679a0ecf4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234726_67e788b63bab12154aa9cbd679a0ecf4.png&h=7fa53cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234742_c31561cd27f5c79abb23d75cccb048fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234742_c31561cd27f5c79abb23d75cccb048fc.png&h=33983a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234746_2261b4695fef599508a4709f6651848e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234746_2261b4695fef599508a4709f6651848e.png&h=8d425af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.把皮蛋切成六份或八份作備用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234753_c4dd7043c556dfe2b1eb1487f5b00e55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234753_c4dd7043c556dfe2b1eb1487f5b00e55.png&h=99c16097&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234811_382e42d13bec72b999e3e239927f361b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234811_382e42d13bec72b999e3e239927f361b.png&h=c75f462e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔴(製作醬汁)步驟：<br />\n1.青尖椒對半切開，並去除裡面的辣椒籽，然後切成粒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234820_734572eabc0ee92e64e163b2b4e76a1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234820_734572eabc0ee92e64e163b2b4e76a1b.png&h=adb493b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234832_b35e1feefcfb79df313eb4e2df1b869d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234832_b35e1feefcfb79df313eb4e2df1b869d.png&h=bd1fcb8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.辣椒切碎、用半紥芫茜切碎、蒜頭切碎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234839_fbdc78bc1fa68c0b462095a5b6d9d85a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234839_fbdc78bc1fa68c0b462095a5b6d9d85a.png&h=4b5af52f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/234852_3f380d5b0705092a70a40c6a1ebdf47f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F234852_3f380d5b0705092a70a40c6a1ebdf47f.png&h=68e2297c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXSzHHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXSzHHa.png&h=61df2078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/235752_795babd4db206679ae4a63984acba171.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F235752_795babd4db206679ae4a63984acba171.png&h=15fdac1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/235757_4d2bb033af79a6f6f105d8eb2812e71b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F235757_4d2bb033af79a6f6f105d8eb2812e71b.png&h=4aafb7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.倒入調味料：兩湯匙浙江醋、兩湯匙生抽、兩至三圈麻油、三至四匙麻辣紅油、稍微撈勻後再加入兩至三匙糖、少許鹽及雞粉<br />\n(如果沒有麻辣紅油，可用辣椒油及花椒油代替)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/082jTPk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F082jTPk.png&h=dbca7bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XnPN2HL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnPN2HL.png&h=075ff3de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0W4Kkuu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0W4Kkuu.png&h=62c9bc62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.把所有調味料撈勻並淋上皮蛋，最後灑上芫茜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EY6kDgj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEY6kDgj.png&h=05bf6d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5iSun3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5iSun3.png&h=e25038da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">完成</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305a0d1a6e09f8ce15180ca9dd67e24a2d08d74e","tid":2231454,"uid":118754,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLNzHKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLNzHKH.jpg&h=1326e842&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"292ced82d4f7b52b55912e970033edd6434b747c","tid":2231454,"uid":375425,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5609f2306884c772451be899f3b61f5cde49c0af","tid":2231454,"uid":24976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:21:42.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完好撚肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f307ee09681095be86003760de649c794a28c2","tid":2231454,"uid":111271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"直接用水洗走皮蛋D灰咪得<br />\n唔洗搞到咁污糟"},{"pid":"a48d1980542b01036d9652386db4bb9266f25994","tid":2231454,"uid":147569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:46:06.000Z","msg":"留名食皮蛋"},{"pid":"aaaf0f2b0c0c0ba26940dc2ae0ccda1d3548106f","tid":2231454,"uid":59659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"講得好慢"},{"pid":"bb03a23dc9f2d8abc62956f342e30dcc01df358f","tid":2231454,"uid":168389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"希望有蒜茸白肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93e5b1fb481ff1ea18c21273000d2c7d2b3c6c5","tid":2231454,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15f307ee09681095be86003760de649c794a28c2","tid":2231454,"uid":111271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"直接用水洗走皮蛋D灰咪得<br />\n唔洗搞到咁污糟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"其實都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過拍片好污糟所以沒咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"becef252bda116697b8920c06cbc91c6c4eab07b","tid":2231454,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaaf0f2b0c0c0ba26940dc2ae0ccda1d3548106f","tid":2231454,"uid":59659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"講得好慢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我會改善下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c33b513403a3b0244088a6e161a2d09080f895e","tid":2231454,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb03a23dc9f2d8abc62956f342e30dcc01df358f","tid":2231454,"uid":168389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"希望有蒜茸白肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"搵日試下，不過整來整去都唔似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b630a3903283da3598c01ee30324e0aac06aa3d3","tid":2231454,"uid":258230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"396e561f759562c03ad022280dfa1115e5808242","tid":2231454,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"樓主手指肥美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5058e93bc9f8434b769abaa76ea6a55125f5cd","tid":2231454,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dis